      "content": "yeah exactly. it's just constant. people talk about \"hope\" like it's a strategy, but it feels more like a delusion to keep us working and consuming while the ship sinks. if the end is inevitable, why does anyone insist on dragging out the process? it feels like there should be a way to just... opt out before the worst part happens.",
